{
  "id": "698743171e0c1e7fc96757e9",
  "title": "bg.iconをCSSで描画するUserCSS",
  "created": 1770472218,
  "updated": 1783333956,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "698743171e0c1e7fc96757e9",
      "text": "bg.iconをCSSで描画するUserCSS",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1770472218,
      "updated": 1770472238
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b5ae600000000000812a9",
      "text": "[bg], [ページを切断する]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783323367,
      "updated": 1783323479
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b5ae600000000000812aa",
      "text": "[UserCSS.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783323367,
      "updated": 1783323367
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b5ae600000000000812ab",
      "text": "井戸端仕様",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783323367,
      "updated": 1783323460
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b5b1c00000000000218f9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783323420,
      "updated": 1783323420
    },
    {
      "id": "698743320000000000c3c53e",
      "text": "from [/nrem-configs/bg.iconをCSSで描画するUserCSS（井戸端仕様）]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1770472243,
      "updated": 1770472246
    },
    {
      "id": "6987435d0000000000c3c53f",
      "text": "from [/customize/改ページ記法]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1770472286,
      "updated": 1770472303
    },
    {
      "id": "6987431a0000000000c3c4fe",
      "text": "from [/nrem-config/セクションの最初の行の行頭にある太字＋をセクション見出し化する]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1770472219,
      "updated": 1770472283
    },
    {
      "id": "6987431a0000000000c3c500",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1770472219,
      "updated": 1770472219
    },
    {
      "id": "6987466f0000000000504a20",
      "text": "参考:  [hr.iconをCSSで描画するUserCSS]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1770473072,
      "updated": 1770473082
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3e464c000000000033c4c5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1782466124,
      "updated": 1782466124
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59180000000000cf673c",
      "text": "[2026-07-06] [改ページ記法]の実装と不具合修正",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322906,
      "updated": 1783331741
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b5ba000000000000218fa",
      "text": "　記法：`[bg.icon][**** title]`",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783323553,
      "updated": 1783331741
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b595d0000000000cf673d",
      "text": "　詳細は[改ページ]を参照のこと",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322975,
      "updated": 1783333956
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3e4a59000000000046a64a",
      "text": "2026-06-26 [疑似背景]が[bg]へのリンクになるように",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1782467161,
      "updated": 1783331757
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3e4aaa000000000046a64b",
      "text": "[2026-06-26] `:has()`を使用しない実装に変更した",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1782467241,
      "updated": 1782467255
    },
    {
      "id": "6987466f0000000000504a21",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1770473072,
      "updated": 1770473072
    },
    {
      "id": "6987431a0000000000c3c501",
      "text": "\tcode:style.css",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1770472219,
      "updated": 1783331733
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59040000000000cf66f8",
      "text": "\t html[data-project-theme=default-minimal] {",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322886,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf66f9",
      "text": "  \t--card-border-width: 1px;",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf66fa",
      "text": "  }",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf66fb",
      "text": "  body {",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf66fc",
      "text": "  \t--virtual-page-margin-top: calc(var(--calculated-paragraph-line-height, 24px) * 3); /* 改ページの間隔（＝疑似背景の縦幅） */",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf66fd",
      "text": "  \t--page-padding-top: 42px;",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf66fe",
      "text": "  \t--page-padding-left: 49px;",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf66ff",
      "text": "  \t--page-padding-bottom: 42px;",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf6700",
      "text": "  \t--page-width: calc(100% + var(--page-padding-left, 49px) * 2);",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf6701",
      "text": "  }",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf6702",
      "text": "  @media(max-width: 767px) {",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf6703",
      "text": "  \tbody {",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf6704",
      "text": "  \t\t--page-padding-top: 28px;",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf6705",
      "text": "  \t\t--page-padding-left: 21px;",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf6706",
      "text": "  \t\t--page-padding-bottom: 42px;",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf6707",
      "text": "  \t}",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf6708",
      "text": "  }",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf6709",
      "text": "  @media(min-width: 768px) and (max-width: 991px) {",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf670a",
      "text": "  \tbody {",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf670b",
      "text": "  \t\t--page-padding-top: 42px;",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf670c",
      "text": "  \t\t--page-padding-left: 42px;",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf670d",
      "text": "  \t\t--page-padding-bottom: 35px;",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf670e",
      "text": "  \t}",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf670f",
      "text": "  }",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf6710",
      "text": "  ",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf6711",
      "text": "  /* [bg.icon] の直後の [**** text] の表示をページタイトルにする */",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf6712",
      "text": "  span:has(> a.icon[href$=\"/bg\"]) + span:not(.indent *) > span > strong.level-4 {",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf6713",
      "text": "  \tdisplay: inline-block;\tfont-weight: 400;\tmargin-bottom: 24px;",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf6714",
      "text": "  }",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf6715",
      "text": "  ",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf6716",
      "text": "  /* [bg.icon]による改ページ */",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf6717",
      "text": "  .line:not(.cursor-line) a.icon[href$=\"/bg\"]:not(.indent *) {",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf6718",
      "text": "  \tdisplay: inline-block;\tbox-sizing: content-box;",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf6719",
      "text": "  \twidth: 100%;",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf671a",
      "text": "  \tmargin-top: var(--page-padding-bottom);",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf671b",
      "text": "  \theight: var(--virtual-page-margin-top);",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf671c",
      "text": "  \tmargin-bottom: var(--page-padding-top);",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf671d",
      "text": "  \t",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf671e",
      "text": "  \tfont-size: 0px; line-height: 0px;",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf671f",
      "text": "  \t& > img.icon[title=\"bg\"] {\theight: 0px !important;\t}",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf6720",
      "text": "  \t",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf6721",
      "text": "  \t/* テロメアを隠す */",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf6722",
      "text": "  \t&::before {",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf6723",
      "text": "  \t\tcontent: \"\";\tdisplay: block;\tposition: absolute;",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf6724",
      "text": "  \t\tbackground-color: var(--page-bg);",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf6725",
      "text": "  \t\ttop: 0;",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf6726",
      "text": "  \t\tleft: calc(-1 * var(--page-padding-left, 49px));",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf6727",
      "text": "  \t\twidth: var(--page-padding-left, 49px);",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf6728",
      "text": "  \t\theight: calc(var(--page-padding-bottom) + var(--virtual-page-margin-top) + var(--page-padding-top));",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf6729",
      "text": "  \t}",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf672a",
      "text": "  \t",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf672b",
      "text": "  \t/* 疑似背景 */",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf672c",
      "text": "  \t&::after {",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf672d",
      "text": "  \t\tcontent: \"\";\tdisplay: block;\tposition: absolute;",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf672e",
      "text": "  \t\ttop: var(--page-padding-bottom);",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf672f",
      "text": "  \t\tborder-top: 4px solid hsl(0 0 0 / 0.16);",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf6730",
      "text": "  \t\tborder-bottom: var(--card-border, unset);",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf6731",
      "text": "  \t\theight: var(--virtual-page-margin-top);",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf6732",
      "text": "  \t\twidth: var(--page-width, 100%);",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf6733",
      "text": "  \t\tleft: calc(-1 * (var(--page-padding-left, 49px) + var(--card-border-width, 0px)) );",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf6734",
      "text": "  \t\tbackground: ",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf6735",
      "text": "  \t\t\tradial-gradient(circle, transparent 20%, var(--B) 20%, var(--B) 80%, transparent 80%, transparent), ",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf6736",
      "text": "  \t\t\tradial-gradient(circle, transparent 20%, var(--B) 20%, var(--B) 80%, transparent 80%, transparent) 50px 50px, ",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf6737",
      "text": "  \t\t\tlinear-gradient(var(--A) 8px, transparent 8px) 0 -4px, linear-gradient(90deg, var(--A) 8px, transparent 8px) -4px 0;",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf6738",
      "text": "  \t\tbackground-color: var(--B, var(--body-bg));",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1783322890,
      "updated": 1783331735
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4b59060000000000cf6739",
